    "name": "Umblight",
    "steam_appid": 3151840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/4e32a52924d7316222d3bcadc29bb741.avif?t=1769623440\" width=780 height=97 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Umblight is a Inscryption-like card game adventure where you're trapped in a dark, machine-filled room that changes as you go. Build your deck of shadow and light cards, make new cards by combining them and play mind-bending synergies as you try to defeat your dungeon master!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/ace97d3abb3540d76375dab14a7e7c40.poster.avif?t=1769623440\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/ace97d3abb3540d76375dab14a7e7c40.webm?t=1769623440\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/ace97d3abb3540d76375dab14a7e7c40.mp4?t=1769623440\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A fast-paced card game based around modern synergistic combos</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategically place and combine your cards on the board</strong>. <strong>Light cards</strong> are defensive and gain a damage blocking shield when you place them, while <strong>shadow cards</strong> damage the opponent through the opponent's cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Card skills</strong> have unique trigger conditions that must be met for them to activate. <strong>Build insane chains of skills</strong> to gain a massive advantage over the enemy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/dda69d10bd10de2fc4af389e3b8e20a0.poster.avif?t=1769623440\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/dda69d10bd10de2fc4af389e3b8e20a0.webm?t=1769623440\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/dda69d10bd10de2fc4af389e3b8e20a0.mp4?t=1769623440\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build your deck of shadow and light cards.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combine and modify your cards to build the most powerful deck you could imagine!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade your player card</strong> with up to 3 abilities that tweak the core of your entire playstyle, but be careful as these abilities always have a downside you'll have to play around.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/ec07c54724fd605c277b4d7c670d45b3.poster.avif?t=1769623440\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/ec07c54724fd605c277b4d7c670d45b3.webm?t=1769623440\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/ec07c54724fd605c277b4d7c670d45b3.mp4?t=1769623440\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Coins are what now?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yeah, they're cards too. Use them as a <strong>free and zero-cost support card</strong> in your battles to <strong>get out of a tight scenario</strong> or to strategically change your cards... or you can just save them to <strong>trade for more powerful cards</strong> at the shop. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/d247954fbafb121ea8d806894cb0ae3b.poster.avif?t=1769623440\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/d247954fbafb121ea8d806894cb0ae3b.webm?t=1769623440\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151840/extras/d247954fbafb121ea8d806894cb0ae3b.mp4?t=1769623440\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your own way</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each playthrough is its own experiment.</strong> Different enemies, rewards, and card synergies will push you to rethink your approach. The core loop rewards creativity: try a new combination, see what clicks, and refine it for the next run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
